<i>noun</i>: 탈 [탈ː], 조난 [조난], 우연 [우연], 사고 [사ː고], 사건 [사ː껀], 불상사 [불쌍사], 돌발 [돌발] <br>
<ul><li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탈 [탈ː]</dt><br>
<dd>1. accident</dd><br>
<dd>전혀 예상하지 못했던 사고.</dd><br>
<dd>An unexpected accident.</dd><br>
<dd>2. disease</dd><br>
<dd>몸에 생긴 병.</dd><br>
<dd>A disease in one’s body.</dd><br>
<dd>3. defect; fault</dd><br>
<dd>결함이나 허물.</dd><br>
<dd>A defect or fault.</dd><br>
<dd>4. breakdown; failure</dd><br>
<dd>기계나 기구, 설비 등의 고장.</dd><br>
<dd>The malfunction of a machine, apparatus, equipment, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>5. excuse; fault</dd><br>
<dd>핑계나 트집.</dd><br>
<dd>An excuse or a fault.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>조난 [조난]</dt><br>
<dd>shipwreck; accident</dd><br>
<dd>항해나 등산 중에 재난을 만남.</dd><br>
<dd>The experience of encountering a disaster while on a voyage or hiking trip.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>우연 [우연]</dt><br>
<dd>chance; accident</dd><br>
<dd>마땅한 이유 없이 어쩌다가 일어난 일.</dd><br>
<dd>Something happened by chance without a proper cause.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사고 [사ː고]</dt><br>
<dd>1. accident</dd><br>
<dd>예상하지 못하게 일어난 좋지 않은 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An unfortunate affair that happens unexpectedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. trouble</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람에게 피해를 주거나 문제를 일으키는 나쁜 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A bad thing that does harm to others or causes a problem</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사건 [사ː껀]</dt><br>
<dd>incident; event; affair; accident; case</dd><br>
<dd>관심이나 주목을 끌 만한 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A matter that is worthy of interest or attention.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>불상사 [불쌍사]</dt><br>
<dd>mishap; scandal; accident</dd><br>
<dd>운이 좋지 않은 나쁜 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An unfortunate, bad affair.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>돌발 [돌발]</dt><br>
<dd>accident; unforeseen incident</dd><br>
<dd>예상하지 못한 일이 갑자기 일어남.</dd><br>
<dd>An incident that happens suddenly and unexpectedly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>